Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:07.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-See you later!\N-Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.92,0:00:12.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shota!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:18.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Are you looking for UFOs again?\N-You don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.90,0:00:20.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's my business!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.71,0:00:24.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We're in the fifth grade now.\NIt's time you gave it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:29.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Why? UFOs really exist.\N-How can you believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.59,0:00:31.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Sure they do!\N-They don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.43,0:00:32.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Do!\N-Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.63,0:00:35.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-lf I say they do, they do!\N-Show me some proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.80,0:00:38.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Right, proof. The proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.48,0:00:42.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Proof, proof, proof, proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.69,0:00:44.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-I'll show you.\N-You're sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.32,0:00:48.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you for sure! For sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.53,0:00:54.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,THE UFO APPEARS!?\NA TOWN IN PANIC!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.11,0:00:56.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.35,0:01:02.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Good morning, Kyoko, Ryoko!\N-You saw the UFO last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.96,0:01:05.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The one in the morning paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:10.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi, don't you read the papers?\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:15.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,A UFO? "Several eyewitnesses\Nin Seika City."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.89,0:01:19.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It says people saw a shiny object\Nflying in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.73,0:01:23.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-That's definitely a UFO!\N-But why the city of Seika?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.90,0:01:26.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What else?\NIt's because St. Tail is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.45,0:01:32.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail is probably\Na messenger from outer space!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.19,0:01:37.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, a thief who roams\Nthe universe, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.57,0:01:42.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,How stupid! Who says\Nshe's a messenger from outer space?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.78,0:01:47.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-What a terrible way to put it.\N-There's no such thing as aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.19,0:01:52.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Then what's this article about?\N-An optical illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.49,0:01:56.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It says many people saw it.\NCan you still call it an illusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:02:00.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,An airplane, a shooting star...\NAnyway, something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:02.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,UFOs aren't scientific!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.75,0:02:05.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Science has yet to prove many things!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:09.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Miss Haneoka, Mr. Asuka.\N-Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.63,0:02:13.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The two of you, use that energy\Nand go do your science homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:15.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.82,0:02:27.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi! Have you heard about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:29.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:34.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,"From the space shuttle to UFOs.\NCosmo World.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.61,0:02:39.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Popular event producer Yuji Kuroda\Nturns the Big Dome into outer space."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.96,0:02:43.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The UFO in the papers,\Na guy took a photo of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.36,0:02:45.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:48.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And that photo will be exhibited\Nat this event.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.08,0:02:52.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're saying you wanna\Ngo and see it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.22,0:02:53.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:58.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If I see it, I'll know if it's real\Nor not. And tomorrow's Sunday...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.73,0:03:02.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Good idea.\NLet's go and check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:06.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Well, now, is this a date?\N-Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.82,0:03:13.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're ready. Go get Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:14.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:17.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Dad, dinner's ready!\N-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:19.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Is he outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:27.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's strange. No one's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:30.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ruby!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.53,0:03:34.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this great?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:38.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It's a new magic trick, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:44.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is much thinner than the piano\Ncord I used. Can't see it, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:48.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ruby, don't struggle.\NDon't struggle so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:54.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Is she all right? Ruby!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:58.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the reeling mechanism\Nneeds more work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:04:01.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.07,0:04:13.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I said that to Seira,\Nbut this is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.72,0:04:15.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:16.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:18.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:24.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's with the sour face?\NSorry we're not Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:27.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ryoko, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.21,0:04:30.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-We heard about it, how it's a date.\N-Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:35.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Can we come along?\N-Well, sure, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:39.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:41.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You guys came along too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.04,0:04:46.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-This has to be enjoyed together.\N-Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:49.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:01.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Not very many people are in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.95,0:05:06.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This model is also cheaply made.\NThere's no detail whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:08.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Where's Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:13.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Now that you mention it...\N-Maybe he's stuck to something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:19.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:23.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Asuka! Let's take a look\Nat the UFO photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:37.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-What's this?\N-"The photos are being enlarged.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:41.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,They will be shown on the last day\Nat the UFO summoning event."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:46.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There, you see? It's a fake\Nso they're delaying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:50.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,No, they're probably having\Nan expert examine the photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:53.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll go ask someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:55.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kuroda, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:59.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're not drawing a crowd.\NAt this rate, we'll be in the red.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:04.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, a turnout will come on\Nthe last day. No one will miss this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.11,0:06:06.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You mean that UFO photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:12.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's fabulous. It's the hottest\Nconversation piece in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.99,0:06:18.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But shouldn't an expert examine it\Nbefore you show it to the public?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.47,0:06:22.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,By the time we do that, the event\Nwill be over. It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:23.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But you--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:26.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,My job is to gather people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.12,0:06:32.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I've planned, along with the photo,\Nan event to summon a real UFO.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:35.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a smash hit, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.57,0:06:39.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Anyway, we're counting on you.\N-Just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:47.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's the man in the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:53.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But, sir, if we enlarge the photo,\Neveryone will know that it's a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:57.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Stupid fool! You're talking too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:06:59.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:04.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Why are you hanging around here?\NHurry up so we can see the UFO--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.47,0:07:09.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-What's wrong?\N-You're the one who stepped on--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.77,0:07:12.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The UFO model's that way.\NLet's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:14.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Kids nowadays are too mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:17.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:23.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about the UFO\Nin the papers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:28.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I want to see a UFO so badly,\NI always carry a camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:33.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But because of that,\Nmy friends make fun of me, so I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.72,0:07:51.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.93,0:07:59.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Wow!\N-That's neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:01.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Is this some sort of hoax?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:05.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's real.\NIt was even in this morning's paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:09.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-It's probably the same UFO.\N-Shota, you've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:11.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:14.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Then it was just\Na remote control airplane?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.27,0:08:19.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I didn't expect it\Nto become such a big sensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.42,0:08:25.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And then my friends took the photo\Nto Cosmo World without me knowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.53,0:08:26.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:29.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And it's going to be\Nexhibited at that event.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:35.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Have you asked for the photo back?\N-Yes, I did! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:42.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,My friends brought it in without\Nmy permission, that UFO photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:44.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.40,0:08:50.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's just the thing for this event,\Nso we're putting it on exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:55.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. It's a fake.\NSo please return it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:59.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Too late now. We already advertised\Nthat it'll be on exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:02.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.47,0:09:06.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You better not tell anyone\Nit's a fake. They'll never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:10.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's unfair. Please return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:15.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll return it to you\Nwhen the event is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.23,0:09:20.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If only I hadn't taken that photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:26.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I understand. Let's pray.\NI'm sure God is with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.82,0:09:29.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I see. So that's the story\Nbehind it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:35.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Shota regrets what he has done\Nand promises not to do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:40.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Okay! The thief St. Tail shall get\Nthat photo back for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:19.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:24.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,"Tonight I'll be stealing\Nthat UFO photo at the Big Dome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.07,0:10:27.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:38.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail is after that photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:43.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes, so we'll be taking care\Nof the security for the photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.54,0:10:45.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I can use him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:51.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I thought that if we could get a photo\Nto reveal St. Tail's identity...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.66,0:10:53.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What would you do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:58.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,An event, of course. With that photo,\Ncrowds will swarm to such an event.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.81,0:11:03.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not! To make\NSt. Tail into such a spectacle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:06.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll leave the security to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.59,0:11:11.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The photograph is set\Nin that slide projector over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:14.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you having it enlarged?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:18.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There are limits to enlarging a photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:21.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We're going to project it\Non a slide, like, bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:25.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've got things to prepare\Nso I'll be on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:31.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Who's gonna let a guy like that\Nreveal St. Tail's identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:40.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:46.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:50.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.05,0:11:54.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:13.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:23.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen,\Nwelcome to Cosmo World!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:28.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,All of you here tonight will\Nwitness a historical event!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.82,0:12:33.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The boy who took the photo we'll\Nbe showing had these words to say:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:38.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,"The UFO will definitely return\Nto retrieve this photo!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.34,0:12:40.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There's more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:45.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We've been informed that St. Tail\Nmight appear to steal this photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.02,0:12:49.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen,\Nhave you brought your cameras?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:53.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What scum, saying a thing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:58.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,For those who photograph a UFO\Nor St. Tail's true identity...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:13:01.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...we have big rewards prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:03.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Now, let us begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:18.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kuroda, there aren't\Nany rewards prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:24.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It'll be hard for anyone to photograph\NSt. Tail's true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.47,0:13:27.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But what if someone\Ndoes photograph her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:29.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll buy it in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:34.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If we have that, I'll surely be able\Nto fill the Big Dome unlike before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.72,0:13:39.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-But what about the UFO?\N-Don't get your hopes up on that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:44.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say that a UFO\Nwill come to retrieve the photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.31,0:13:50.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Just an act to arouse the audience.\NAnd that photo, it looks like a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:54.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's a problem!\NLet's cancel the event right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:56.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:14:00.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The only one who will be criticized\Nis the boy who took the photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:03.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We're only victims of a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:07.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And luck is on our side if\Na crowd gathers, am I not right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.92,0:14:09.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,How could you--?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.17,0:14:17.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Mommy, when is the UFO coming?\N-I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.74,0:14:20.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-It won't come, will it?\N-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:23.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Hurry up and summon the UFO!\N-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:25.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is where we end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:33.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It looks like our UFO has decided\Nto make a sidetrack somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.78,0:14:38.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,While we're waiting for its arrival,\Nwe'll present the UFO photo--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.82,0:14:40.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's the UFO!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:44.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The UFO appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:47.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,A picture, a picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:49.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We can get the reward!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.31,0:14:51.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.31,0:14:55.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Could it be a real UFO?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:15:00.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's St. Tail! After her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:03.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! St. Tail has appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:05.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:06.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Where, where?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:10.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and turn on the lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:14.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-No good! The switch won't connect!\N-Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:16.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:18.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She's over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:20.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't let her escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:28.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Are you all right, Asuka Jr.?\N-Never mind me, get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:29.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:33.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There she is! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:35.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.61,0:15:40.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.29,0:15:51.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail! This is\Nwhere the chase ends!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:54.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-What's going on here?\N-I can't see a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:59.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The flash won't reach\Nfrom this far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:01.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is just fabulous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:06.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kuroda! This is big trouble!\NA UFO has really appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.10,0:16:11.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do?\NYou know there aren't any rewards!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:14.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-What's that?\N-Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.43,0:16:23.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:27.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...showtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.75,0:16:33.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:53.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Well, Asuka Jr., I'll be\Nleaving with the photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:56.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Darn! Don't think\NI'll let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:17:01.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Stop it! Let go of me!\N-I won't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:04.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand this, you pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:09.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-I'm not a--\N-Never mind! Just let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:16.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.49,0:17:25.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.53,0:17:29.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That hurts. I shouldn't use\Nexperimental devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:34.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hold it! Just as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:37.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.42,0:17:43.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Open this door! I've taken a picture!\N-Give me my reward!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:51.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-What is your plan now, Kuroda?\N-Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:54.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:10.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hope you get a picture\Nof a real UFO next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:12.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:18.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,How did you get that photograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.10,0:18:22.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-It fell from the sky.\N-From the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:27.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's a fake.\NI was in trouble because...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:31.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...they forced me to have it\Nrevealed at the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.76,0:18:34.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:37.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,So that's why. St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:47.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Asuka Jr. There was\Nanother UFO appearance, wasn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.09,0:18:52.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That was just one of St. Tail's\Ntricks. UFOs don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:55.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You still don't believe?\NYou're stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:18:58.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,In the first place,\Nanti-scientific things--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:03.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-What is it? What's the matter?\N-That.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:09.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Was that a--?\N-UFO?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:11.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Wasn't it?\N-Guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:16.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
